mart original ideas from one and all we are looking for a talented professional who is proactive proficient and who will enjoy coming up with editorial graphics as well as ideas for visualbased stories and series the ideal candidate will be highly skilled in photoshop and illustrator javascript html motion graphics andor animation experience is a plus the designer will be responsible for generating artistic and eyecatching images to be used as featured images for stories on the site as well as embedded graphics and text treatments these will run the gamut from unique infographics and data visualizations to photobased portraiture all while being faithful to salon’s voice and brand a link to a diverse portfolio showing a command of creative data visualization is required please send application materials and linkedin profile to artsaloncom about salon press ways to get salon contact and help staff diversity jobs submissions advertise on salon awards investor relations salon comments privacy policy terms of service corrections dmca policy earnings press releases and news corporate governance copyright   salon media group inc reproduction of material from any salon pages without written permission is strictly prohibited salon ® is registered in the us patent and trademark office as a trademark of salon media group inc associated press articles copyright   the associated press all rights reserved this material may not be published broadcast rewritten or redistributed salon indepth news politics business technology  culture salon career advice for spicey sean spicer probably got me fired at cbs i wound up stocking shelves at night and learned things hell never know bob hennelly top stories most recent checkpoint usa crossing the border into trump’s america a bizarre encounter with an angry paranoid border agent gives us a taste of what we missed living abroad jonathan meador sunday jul    pm edt politics border agent border patrol “game of thrones” recap “stormborn” demon