 bloggers on june   salon closed its online chat board table talk without stating an official reason for ending that section of the site on july   salon announced that it will be featuring content from mondoweiss in september  salon media group sold the well to the group of members business model and operations salon has been unprofitable through its entire history since  the company has been dependent on ongoing cash injections from board chairman john warnock and william hambrecht father of former salon ceo elizabeth hambrecht during the nine months ended december   these cash contributions amounted to  million compared to revenue in the same period of  million aspects of the saloncom site offerings ordered by advancing date free content around  new articles posted perday revenues wholly derived from inpage advertisements perday new content was reduced for a time salon premium subscription approximately  percent of new content was made available to subscribers only other subscription benefits included free magazines and adfree viewing larger more conspicuous ad units introduced for nonsubscribers a hybrid subscription model readers now can read content by viewing a second full screen advertisement to earn a day pass or gain access by subscribing to salon premium salon core after salon premium subscriptions declined from about  to  it was rebranded in  as salon core subscriptions featuring a different mix of benefits controversy in march  while otto warmbier was imprisoned in north korea the site posted an article about warmbier called this might be america’s biggest idiot frat boy meet the uva student who thought he could pull a prank in north korea after warmbiers death the article was subsequently removed andrew ohehir the executive editor of salon said that the article was based on the opinions of larry wilmore references  saloncom site overview alexa internet retrieved august     saloncom whois dns  domain info  domaintools whois retrieved    the fall of saloncom politico  march    the new salon – very different from the old salon politico media retrieved    note to liberal media outlets opposition to syrian refugees is not a fringe position washington post retrieved    kurtz howard  salon’s clickbait strategy the phantom fight against fox news fox news retrieved    form q securities and exchange commission   bloomgardensmoke kara june   kerry lauerman is leaving salon dave daley named interim editor in chief the new york observer   marr dave february   salon editor david daley first willsongrady digital media fellow grady college   walsh joan  november  im not leaving salon salon archived from the original on december   retrieved  december    about salon salon   farhi paul march  can salon make it ajrarchiveorg american journalism review retrieved may     a b open salon staff march   news about open salon open salon   interview with saloncoms david talbot journalismjobscom june  archived from the original on august   retrieved april     a b calderone michael september   salon ceo calls for american spring with sites relaunch huffington post retrieved october     form k salon media group inc us securities and exchange commission  july  retrieved  july    sutton kelsey may   incoming salon ceo signals big changes ahead politico   a b herhold scott december   net magazine salon epitomizes fate of mind over matter san jose mercury news archived from the original on february   retrieved    pogash carol  cyberspace journalism american journalism review archived from the original on december   retrieved    adam begley reading bytes san francisco magazine formerly san francisco focus october  p   the best web sites of  time retrieved july     salon internet inc wwwnasdaqcom retrieved    saloncom wins credibility online with intelligent and stylish content los angeles times issn  retrieved    lauerman kerry july   welcome to our public beta opensaloncom archived from the original on april   retrieved april     lauerman kerry mar